"""
Section {{ section_num }} вЂ” Input validation and edge cases.

Uses {{ entity.name }} as the primary test entity.
Requires ctx.state: {{ auth_entity.name_lower if auth_entity else 'user' }}1_token.
Populates ctx.state: long_title_{{ entity.name_lower }}_id, xss_{{ entity.name_lower }}_id, unicode_{{ entity.name_lower }}_id
